<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>Privacy Policy - Clario</title>
<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen bg-gray-950 text-white">
<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
<a href="/" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 mb-8 inline-block">&larr; Back to Clario</a>

<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
<p class="text-gray-400 mb-8">Last updated: December 12, 2024</p>

<div class="prose prose-invert prose-gray max-w-none space-y-8">

<section>
<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-white">1. Overview</h2>
<p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">Clario ("we", "our", "us") respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect information when you use our visual explanation generator service at getclario.net.</p>
</section>

<section>
<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-white">2. Information We Collect</h2>

<h3 class="text-xl font-medium mb-3 text-white mt-6">Information You Provide</h3>
<ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-300 space-y-2">
<li><strong>Text Prompts:</strong> The descriptions you enter to generate visual content</li>
<li><strong>Payment Information:</strong> When you purchase unlimited access, payment is processed by Lemon Squeezy. We do not store your credit card details.</li>
</ul>

<h3 class="text-xl font-medium mb-3 text-white mt-6">Automatically Collected Information</h3>
<ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-300 space-y-2">
<li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Number of generations, styles used, timestamps</li>
<li><strong>Device Information:</strong> Browser type, operating system (via standard web logs)</li>
<li><strong>Local Storage:</strong> We use browser localStorage to track your free generation count and paid status. This data stays on your device.</li>
</ul>
</section>

<section>
<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-white">3. How We Use Information</h2>
<ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-300 space-y-2">
<li>To provide and improve the Service</li>
<li>To process your generations and deliver results</li>
<li>To track usage limits (free tier)</li>
<li>To process payments (via Lemon Squeezy)</li>
<li>To respond to support requests</li>
<li>To analyze usage patterns and improve the Service</li>
</ul>
</section>

<section>
<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-white">4. Data Retention</h2>
<p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed"><strong>Prompts:</strong> Text prompts may be logged for quality improvement and abuse prevention. We do not permanently store the generated images on our servers - they are delivered to you and then deleted.</p>
<p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mt-4"><strong>Payment Records:</strong> Transaction records are maintained by Lemon Squeezy according to their privacy policy and applicable financial regulations.</p>
</section>

<section>
<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-white">5. Third-Party Services</h2>
<p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">We use the following third-party services:</p>
<ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-300 mt-4 space-y-2">
<li><strong>Google AI (Gemini):</strong> Powers the image generation. Prompts are sent to Google's API. See Google's Privacy Policy.</li>
<li><strong>Lemon Squeezy:</strong> Processes payments. See Lemon Squeezy's Privacy Policy.</li>
<li><strong>Vercel:</strong> Hosts the website. See Vercel's Privacy Policy.</li>
</ul>
</section>

<section>
<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-white">6. Cookies and Local Storage</h2>
<p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">We use browser localStorage (not cookies) to:</p>
<ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-300 mt-4 space-y-2">
<li>Track your remaining free generations</li>
<li>Remember your paid/unlocked status</li>
</ul>
<p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mt-4">This data is stored locally in your browser and is not transmitted to our servers. You can clear this data by clearing your browser's local storage.</p>
</section>

<section>
<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-white">7. Data Security</h2>
<p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">We implement reasonable security measures to protect your information. All data transmission uses HTTPS encryption. However, no method of transmission over the Internet is 100% secure.</p>
</section>

<section>
<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-white">8. Your Rights</h2>
<p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">Depending on your location, you may have rights regarding your personal data, including:</p>
<ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-300 mt-4 space-y-2">
<li>Access to your data</li>
<li>Correction of inaccurate data</li>
<li>Deletion of your data</li>
<li>Data portability</li>
</ul>
<p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mt-4">To exercise these rights, contact us at support@getclario.net.</p>
</section>

<section>
<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-white">9. Children's Privacy</h2>
<p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">The Service is not intended for children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you believe we have collected information from a child under 13, please contact us.</p>
</section>

<section>
<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-white">10. Changes to This Policy</h2>
<p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.</p>
</section>

<section>
<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-white">11. Contact</h2>
<p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">For privacy-related questions, contact us at: support@getclario.net</p>
</section>

</div>

<div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-gray-800 flex gap-6">
<a href="/" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300">&larr; Back to Clario</a>
<a href="/terms" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-300">Terms of Service</a>
</div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
